<P>
ULAN BATOR, March 27 (Xinhua) -- Mongolia's ruling National
Democratic Party Chairman Tsakhiya Elbegdorj said Friday a merger
between his party and the Social Democratic Party would be in the
best interests of both the party and the country.
</P>
