Kiriyenko at the head of a new cabinet, Yeltsin said on national
radio.
</P>
<P>
After Yeltsin dismissed the government on March 23, Kiriyenko
was appointed acting prime mnister and nominated to take the
office on Friday.
</P>
<P>
