<HEADLINE> S.Korea to Make Efforts Against Increasing Crimes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SEOUL, March 27 (Xinhua) -- South Korea said Friday that it
will spare no efforts in its fight against increasing crimes and
maintaining stability amid the on-going economic crisis.
</P>
<P>
